# MetWithStrangers Signaling Server URL
# Set this to your deployed Cloudflare Worker WebSocket URL.
# After deploying: npm run deploy (in Backend/), then use the URL shown.
# Example:
VITE_SIGNALING_URL=wss://whychat-switchboard.lenovoideapubg.workers.dev
#
# Leave empty to run in demo mode (fully self-contained, no backend needed).
# VITE_SIGNALING_URL=
